These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Flower: amaryllis, lily, daisy, rose
Birthday: january, august, february, june
1. Flower:amaryllis is on the right of Birthday:february##1
2. Birthday:june is on the far left##1
3. Birthday:february is between Birthday:august and Flower:lily##2
4. Flower:rose is on the far left##1
5. Flower:daisy is between Flower:lily and Flower:amaryllis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Flower   | rose         | lily   | daisy | amaryllis       |
| Birthday      | june | january | february   | august |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Job: mechanic, journalist, dancer, paramedic
Sport: badminton, soccer, snowboarding, sailing
1. Sport:sailing is between Job:dancer and Sport:soccer##2
2. Job:paramedic is on the far right##1
3. Sport:snowboarding is on the right of Sport:badminton##1
4. Job:mechanic is on the left of Sport:badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Job         | journalist | mechanic | dancer | paramedic |
| Sport   | soccer    | sailing   | badminton | snowboarding       |

