.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Color: black, emerald, azure, chestnut
City: hamburg, berlin, boston, rome
1. City:boston is on the right of Color:chestnut##1
2. City:boston is between City:berlin and Color:emerald##2
3. City:berlin is on the far left##1
4. City:rome is on the left of Color:azure##1
5. Color:emerald == City:rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Color          | chestnut    | black | emerald   | azure  |
| City   | berlin | boston   | rome | hamburg |

